HEADWORD: Warsaw
<hw>War"saw</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<sd>(a)</sd> <def>The black grouper (<spn>Epinephelus nigritus</spn>) of
the southern coasts of the United States.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>The
jewfish; -- called also <altname>guasa</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
